The Rugby Africa Gold Cup (www.RugbyAfrique.com/rugby-news/) takes a break to pave way for the Rugby Sevens World Cup. This week on the review segment Damima Duffield and Ng'arua Kamuya do a postmortem of the first half of the 2018 Rugby Africa Gold Cup. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Rugby Africa. Media Contact: Rugby@APO-opa.org Media filesDownload logo Multimedia content Video: Official Podcast for the 2018 Africa Gold Cup: Review Show